10. The non-transitory computer readable medium of claim 6, wherein the training of the first machine learning algorithm uses a first dataset, and the provided indication comprises a suggestion to avoid the predicted delay by using a substitute smaller dataset that is predicted to shorten processing time instead of the first dataset.
